# CoreX storage - gcs

This package provides an implementation of the CoreX storage interface for gcs.

## Installation
~~~bash
pip install corex-storage-gcs
~~~

## Usage
~~~python
from corex_storage_gcs.handler import GcsHandler
handler = GcsHandler()
handler.example_method()
~~~
